name: Cottage Garden (Sam and Daisy) #1A
description: Sam and Daisy are preparing to take their puppy out for a walk. There is a light breeze causing the flowers and leaves to sway. Giant bees have been attracted to the numerous flowers and plants in the garden. Snails are crawling on the moss infested walls of their cottage. Mynas have also perched onto the roof and are making a lot of noise. Some chickens are feeding near the hay stack.
